title: Elvis Presley - Elvis Sings... [2014]  (Flac) [FrankFoo]
description:
Elvis Presley - Elvis Sings... [2014]  (Flac)

Elvis Sings is a 23 track compilation of one of the greatest, most recognisable voices of all time covering much-loved hits from his superstar contemporaries such as Chuck Berry, Ray Charles, Neil Diamond and Bob Dylan. 

A genre-spanning collection of songs get a new twist with vocals from Elvis on classic tracks such as 'You've Lost That Loving Feeling', 'Bridge Over Troubled Water' and 'My Way'. 

This release is a great way to discover the versatile voice of Elvis who could apply his unique vocal stylings to any material.

Genre: Rock
